 detection, at 2.1$\\sigma$\nsignificance, of the filaments in the SZ signal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Oct 2019 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 10:41:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
